<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَعِل بكَسْر العين، يفعَل بفتحها<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[س]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[دَخِس]</span>: الدَّخَس: داءٌ يأخُذُ الدّابَّةَ في قوائِمها، وفَرَس دَحِسٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ش]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[دَخِش]</span>: الدَّخَش: حكَى بعضُهم:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">دَخِشَ دَخَشاً:</span> إِذا امْتَلأ لحْماً: ومنه اشْتقاق دَخْشَم.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وبعضُ أهْلِ اليَمن يقولُ:</span> دَخِشَ العَظم <span class="c2">«١»</span>: إِذا تَفتَّتَ وبَلِيَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[دَخِنَتِ]</span> النّارُ: إِذا ارْتَفَع دُخانها.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">ودَخِنَ الطّعامُ:</span> عَلِقَ به الدُّخان، ودَخِنَ الطَّبيخ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>ورَجُلٌ دَخِن <span class="c2">«٢»</span> الخُلُق.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وفي الحديث <span class="c2">«٣»</span>: <span class="c2">«هُدنة على دَخِنِ»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> اسْتقرارْ على أمورٍ مكرْوهة.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">ويُقال:</span> الدَّخَنُ: الحقد.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">والدُّخْنَةُ من الألوانِ:</span> كُدْرَةٌ في سَواد:<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">يقالُ:</span> شاةٌ دَخْناء وكَبْشٌ أدخنُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>... الزّيادَة<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
